      "narration_text": "Four steps. First: email hr@humanitarians.ai and you'll receive the toolkit and access. Second: copy the dot-env example file and fill in your keys. Third: run setup dash dash install. Fourth: run dot-slash-art keys. If everything shows green, you're ready to build.",
